        "TileImage": "$($repository a7fd7a4f-2bee-4787-bc60-90f9dd64233b).Image",
        "Description": "Hello? Hitman 4-7? This is Diana Burnwood from ICA and I want to help you. I know something about  Zaydan. He&apos;s working with Novikov. Novikov found out about you after Zaydan started investigating him, and convinced Zaydan to turn on you, and as a reward, he would give him ultimate Power. I know where ICA keeps its files and client data. Chongqing, China. Kill the Director, Imogen Royce, and Board member Angus Pritchard. Good luck.\r\r[REMAKE OF PS CONTRACT BY &quot;ContractsAgency&quot;]",
